{"tid":579032,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] MMORPG黑色沙漠mobile","createTime":"2018-03-03T08:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T23:38:29.000Z","uid":69556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e91a2b5d42338241917d6bb51a53e95ee67e26b7","tid":579032,"uid":69556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T08:24:01.000Z","msg":"　　韓國遊戲研發商 PearlAbyss 改編自旗下知名線上遊戲《黑色沙漠》的手機遊戲新作《黑色沙漠 Mobile》（iOS / Android）已於 2 月 28 日在韓國正式上架。本作於韓國實施事前登錄以來獲得許多玩家關注，預約人數突破 400 萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/96/8fe0bbc4c921551246f9a37283103rk5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F96%2F8fe0bbc4c921551246f9a37283103rk5.JPG&h=2462b5e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n　　《黑色沙漠 Mobile》是一款手機平台的動作 MMORPG，主打與 PC 線上遊戲同樣華麗的動作以及擬真的高畫質，在「角色創造」的自由度上面也與 PC 版同樣有所要求，玩家甚至可透過觸控調整臉形、眼形、鼻型、唇形等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/98/79f18134356c2a3814740a2bb9103rm5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F98%2F79f18134356c2a3814740a2bb9103rm5.JPG&h=e468e883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n　　身為一款動作角色扮演遊戲，玩家可選擇戰士、遊俠、巨人、巫師、女武神等多種職業，在技能樹以及戰鬥打擊感方面也多所著墨。除了戰鬥以及公會系統之外，遊戲內也包括採集、釣魚等遊戲內容。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/90/43fecac326c2beda40f6bedf3e103re5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F90%2F43fecac326c2beda40f6bedf3e103re5.JPG&h=d29c601c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/93/b81e46b32c801bb0a201e4af78103rh5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F93%2Fb81e46b32c801bb0a201e4af78103rh5.JPG&h=d3959b14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n　　《黑色沙漠 Mobile》已於韓國上架，目前尚未有在台上市的確切計畫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n※ 本作目前僅於韓國地區推出。<br />\n<br />\nios下載: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/kr/app/id1323002999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fkr%2Fapp%2Fid1323002999&d=7iYbtcZZeJhd3jzdZBIOaTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=dcedb958\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/kr/app/id1323002999</a><br />\n<br />\nandroid下載: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pearlabyss.blackdesertm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.pearlabyss.blackdesertm&d=7iYbtcZZeJhd3jzdZBIOaTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=35a6b230\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pearlabyss.blackdesertm</a>"},{"pid":"69b5ddc1789403516e98eb225d33f0511e1b4b34","tid":579032,"uid":69556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T08:24:49.000Z","msg":"有冇人都有玩?"},{"pid":"722f65d2d53ee08fb66279cccaf7d602cb018efa","tid":579032,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T08:42:18.000Z","msg":"萬能KEY:<br />\n<br />\n去到台灣一定特別版<br />\n去到日本一定鎖國版<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1575cda9a8fecbdeedc221f53877648a04c91e9d","tid":579032,"uid":69556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"722f65d2d53ee08fb66279cccaf7d602cb018efa","tid":579032,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T08:42:18.000Z","msg":"萬能KEY:<br />\n<br />\n去到台灣一定特別版<br />\n去到日本一定鎖國版<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T08:53:57.000Z","msg":"所以唔等台灣版<br />\n唔想見到第二個天堂m<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19966dbaf78238353bde66bdc201fc22a622b3f","tid":579032,"uid":6233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T09:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9232604d65d9ec1243aa44ded5278ae88cbd669c","tid":579032,"uid":89025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T09:21:42.000Z","ms